    • Constructor Detail

      • FoodItem

        public FoodItem​(java.lang.String name,
                long catalogueNumber,
                int quantity,
                Date productionDate,
                Date expiryDate,
                int minTemperature,
                int maxTemperature,
                int price)
        Creates a new FoodItem object
        Parameters:
        name - the name of the food item (cannot be empty)
        catalogueNumber - the catalogue number of the food item (must be at least 4 digits)
        quantity - the amount of food items of this type (must be 0 or higher)
        productionDate - date of production (cannot be after expiration date)
        expiryDate - date of expiration (cannot be before production date)
        minTemperature - the minimum temperature this food item can be stored in (cannot be higher than max temperature)
        maxTemperature - the maximum temperature this food item can be stored in (cannot be lower than min temperature)
        price - the price for this food item (cannot be lower than 1)
